com.jidesoft.swing
Interface Prioritized

public interface Prioritized

An interface to indicate something that has priority. The priority is just an int value. Although it is up to developer to decide whihc priority value is higher than the other, we suggest the higher value, the higher priority with 0 means default priority when priority is not specified.

Method Summary

          Gets the priority.

Gets the priority. The value could be from Integer.MIN_VALUE to Integer.MAX_VALUE with 0 as the default priority.
